“An elite British boarding school turns into a battleground for survival when seismic tremors unleash unspeakable horrors.” And Simon Pegg and Nick Frost are in it? Sign me up!


Slaughterhouse Rulez stars Pegg, Frost, Asa Butterfield, Michael Sheen, Margot Robbie, Finn Cole, and Hermione Corfield. The film is directed by Crispian Mills (A Fantastic Fear of Everything).


Slaughterhouse Rulez releases to select theaters and digital on May 17, 2019.
